I've definitely seen twitch carry games recently. But I'm surprised that they aren't going after Jinx before him.

She's been popping off insanely hard in all my games. Her damage is ridiculous right now. Champion GG lists her as the #2 ADC right now, right behind Kog.

IMO, all the "late game" ADCs (i.e. ADCs with strong steroids or high AS) are a little strong right now. {{champion:96}} {{champion:222}} {{champion:29}} even {{champion:18}}
